nhc_headline: ...GABRIELLE STILL STRUGGLING OVER THE CENTRAL ATLANTIC...
summary: ...GABRIELLE STILL STRUGGLING OVER THE CENTRAL ATLANTIC... As of 11:00 AM AST Thu Sep 18 the center of Gabrielle was located near 20.3, -51.7 with movement WNW at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1004 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
